OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fcloudy, damp and in places murky
OL,7,Fevening, with fog patches on the
OL,8,Fhills. Turning drier overnight, but
OL,9,Fcloud may be thick enough for light
OL,10,Fdrizzle on hills. Staying rather
OL,11,Fcloudy, but mild with a light breeze.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTuesday:FTuesday will start cloudy and
OL,14,Fbreezy with patchy light rain, chiefly
OL,15,Fin the west. Brighter spells
OL,16,Fdeveloping during the day, especially
OL,17,Fin the east where it will become very
OL,18,Fmild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
